comments: Harden (LAC) initiates contact with Sengun's (HOU) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Zubac (LAC) legally contests Smith Jr.'s (HOU) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Smith Jr.'s (HOU) shot attempt does not make contact with the rim and the shot clock expires.
Leonard (LAC) is firming up over to his left leg in VanVleet's (HOU) path and does not deliver illegal contact during the pick.
Smith Jr. (HOU) moves alongside Harden's (LAC) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
George (LAC) brings his left hand forward to cleanly block Green's (HOU) driving shot attempt.
Sengun (HOU) establishes himself in George's (LAC) path and his legs remain within the frame of his body as contact occurs, which he does not deliver.
Leonard (LAC) initiates contact to Green's (HOU) wrist and the contact causes him to lose control of the ball.
Sengun (HOU) brings his right hand forward and brushes Zubac's (LAC) arm as marginal contact occurs during Zubac's dunk attempt.
Leonard (LAC) deflects the ball out of bounds.
Leonard (LAC) jumps and initiates contact to Sengun's (HOU) body that affects his shot attempt in the post.
Smith Jr. (HOU) attempts to move around the screen by Powell (LAC) and marginal contact occurs that does not dislodge him from his screening position.
Tate (HOU) moves forward into Harden's (LAC) space as he contests the jump shot attempt and makes contact with his lower body that affects Harden's ability to return to the floor.
Brooks (HOU) commits a take foul on Leonard (LAC).
